author: Alan Dawson
description: Manchester United defeated Ajax by a 2-0 score in a Europa League final at the Friends Arena in Stockholm on Wednesday, two days after a bombing in Manchester.
title: Manchester United triumph over Ajax in emotional Europa League final

description: Desperate parents and friends have been searching frantically for loved ones as young as eight years old following the terror attack on the Ariana Grande concert at the Manchester Arena on Monday night.
title: Ariana Grande concert attack: 8-year-old among those feared missing in Manchester

author: Andrew Griffin
description: Martyn Hett, a young man who died in the terror attack at Manchester Arena, was beloved on the internet. Mr Hett was 29 years old and was described as “iconic and beautiful” by his friend Russell Hayward, who announced his death. “He left this world exactly how he lived, centre of attention,” Mr Hayward wrote. The young PR manager had hundreds of friends – and thousands of loving fans online, after a series of appearances on TV.
title: Martyn Hett died in the Manchester attack. He was one of the internet's most favourite people

author: Niamh McIntyre
description: Family and friends are turning to social media in a desperate bid to locate loved ones who are still missing after a terror attack near Manchester Arena last night. Twenty-two people are confirmed dead and fifty-nine injured after an explosion ripped through crowds as they left an Ariana Grande concert.
title: Desperate families are sharing photos of their missing loved ones after the Manchester attack
